                         Work phone: 603-881-2743
                         Home phone: 603-886-6540


          DIRECTIONS TO:

                               Crowne Plaza Hotel
                               2 Somerset Parkway
                        Nashua, New Hampshire 03063-1036


          FROM NORTH OF NASHUA:  Take 293 South to Route 3 South
          (Everett Turnpike).  Take 3 South to Exit 8.  Proceed with
          GENERAL DIRECTIONS below.


          FROM SOUTH OF NASHUA:  Take 495 towards Lowell,
          Massachusetts.  At Lowell, take Route 3 North (towards New
          Hampshire) to Exit 8.  Proceed with GENERAL DIRECTIONS
          below.


          GENERAL DIRECTIONS:  From Route 3, Exit 8:  Make a left turn
          at the second set of traffic lights into Trafalgar Square.
          The Crowne Plaza is on your left.


          FROM MANCHESTER AIRPORT:  When exiting the airport, turn
          right onto Brown Avenue.  Take Brown to Route 293 North.
          From Route 293, take the exit for Route 3 South (Everett
          Turnpike).  Take Route 3 to Exit 8.  Proceed with GENERAL
          DIRECTIONS above.


          FROM NEW YORK CITY:  Take I-95 North to New Haven, CT.  In
          New Haven, exit onto I-91 North.  Follow I-91 North to
          Hartford, CT.  Then exit onto I-84 east to Sturbridge, MA
          and the Massachusetts Turnpike (I-90).  Take the turnpike
          east 10 miles to Exit 10, Route 290.  Take Route 290 east
          though Worcester, MA to Route 495 North.  Proceed with FROM
          SOUTH OF NASHUA directions above.  (Total travel time from
          New York is approximately 5 hours.)
